      "Another company found that the AI invoice processor was actually faster AND more accurate than their manual process — but only for domestic invoices. Import invoices with customs documentation had a 15% error rate. The honest approach: deploy the agent for domestic invoices (where it delivers clear value) and keep humans on import invoices (while training the agent further in shadow mode).",
      "This is what real AI ROI measurement looks like. No magic numbers. No inflated claims. Just measured results, honest assessment, and incremental deployment. If that sounds like the right approach for your organization, we would love to set up a pilot.",
