      "**Stage 2: Bank Reconciliation (Account Aggregator)** — The Recon Agent fetches bank statements through India's Account Aggregator framework via Finvu. This is RBI-regulated and consent-based — each client explicitly approves data sharing through Finvu's consent UI. The agent matches invoice amounts to bank debits using narration parsing and amount matching. Our implementation achieves high auto-match rate (measured during pilot)s.",
